{"tid":1234781,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"你哋同情黑警?","createTime":"2019-06-17T03:57:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T01:38:49.000Z","uid":186807,"like":4,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f51aaaca7513d9575476942054080f95a185c291","tid":1234781,"uid":186807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T03:57:16.000Z","msg":"唔該大家，停一停，諗一諗。<br />\n你哋同情黑警?<br />\n諗下班學生俾人打成點?<br />\n諗下幾多人被捕，被控告?<br />\n諗下死咗嗰位義士。<br />\n無黑警咁盡力幫手，你估林鄭一個人可以完事?<br />\n打完，拉完，有人工加，公平咩?<br />\n影曬相，舉曬V字咁。你同情佢?<br />\n記唔記得個伯伯俾人射到訓低。<br />\n佢哋連個手無寸鐵嘅伯伯都照射，仲要告佢阿。<br />\n你哋同情佢?<br />\n記唔記得個老師俾黑警射頭，差啲啲就盲㗎啦，又係俾人拉，又要等被控告暴動。<br />\n記唔記得班黑警沖埋去醫院拉人?<br />\n值得同情咩?<br />\n<br />\n0<br />\n<br />\n0"},{"pid":"0a9a6b1cf918ab0ac5415f75450650d6324fc33f","tid":1234781,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T03:57:48.000Z","msg":"push 追究黑警"},{"pid":"be475d48351d086a0f96c4bdd7a855e2c5a1451e","tid":1234781,"uid":16372,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T04:04:43.000Z","msg":"NEVER!!"},{"pid":"b7772f1ce19a9ab99412b780d7899c58fd6a7fd1","tid":1234781,"uid":263234,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T04:05:25.000Z","msg":"黑警必須解散!"},{"pid":"13f6976d15cc53b61f05e91accf3770e2a066790","tid":1234781,"uid":25391,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T04:07:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">冇可能啊</span></span>"},{"pid":"0836f19557148b444779dda97987da9e9f146fa4","tid":1234781,"uid":186807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T05:12:34.000Z","msg":"推上去"},{"pid":"8339c33920e223836d57ebd36604c23a8eb29ee2","tid":1234781,"uid":186807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T07:43:50.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7b82ac9da86693cfc1523a312fa3f2975f807d8b","tid":1234781,"uid":84088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T07:56:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪